Accessing Small SkewLeftBrace AllSmallSkewLeftBrace is an accessor function for accessing the complete list of non-isomorphic skewleftbrace models from orders 2 to 3.
The models are generated by Mace4 , using the definitions in Section .

Definition of SkewLeftBrace formulas(SkewLeftBrace).
x+(y*z) = ((x+y)*a(x))*(x+z).
end_of_list.
